{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "f2045388-2b10-49d1-ad31-d2cb1feb38f8", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f2045388-2b10-49d1-ad31-d2cb1feb38f8@1.pkg/1772597672706/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597672926", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f2045388-2b10-49d1-ad31-d2cb1feb38f8@1.pkg/1772597672706/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597672926"}, "identifier": "f2045388-2b10-49d1-ad31-d2cb1feb38f8", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"margin-left: 0.15in;text-align: left;vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">本题考查养成健康的生活方式。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.15in;text-align: left;vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">A:</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">高糖高脂食品易导致肥胖、高血压等慢性病，合理控制此类食品符合健康生活要求；故</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">A</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">说法错误；</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.15in;text-align: left;vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">B:</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">规律锻炼能增强体质、控制体重，是防治慢性病的有效途径，故</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">B</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">说法正确；</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.15in;text-align: left;vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">C</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">：过量生冷辛辣食物可能刺激肠胃，不利于身体健康；故</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">C</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">说法错误；</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0.15in;text-align: left;vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">D：</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">药物减肥存在副作用风险，中学生应通过科学饮食和运动管理体重，而非依赖药物，故</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">D</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">说法错误；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">故本题选</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">B</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）&ldquo;体重管理年&rdquo;是国家卫生健康委联合教育部、体育总局等16个部门开展的活动，旨在普及健康生活方式，加强慢性病防治。管理好体重，中学生应（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）“体重管理年”是国家卫生健康委联合教育部、体育总局等16个部门开展的活动，旨在普及健康生活方式，加强慢性病防治。管理好体重，中学生应（   ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f2045388-2b10-49d1-ad31-d2cb1feb38f8@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755250440483", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_i